<p>周末</p>
<p>银川断崖式降温</p>
<p>最低温仅有-13℃</p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201210/629a9e7a27454ecba8b22bfc06d23bc4.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
